Amanye amalungu eNdlu yoWiso-mthetho aye azingomb' isifuba ngelithi amagama awo aza kutshintshwa abe ziiMember of the Welsh Parliament (MWP).
Oku kwabangelwa kukuba, iCawa yayisaziwa ngokuba yiWelsh Parliament.
Ngoku, amalungu aseburhulumenteni avela kwimimandla eyahlukeneyo yepolitiki ayoyika ukuba isibizo esitsha siza kubenza babe zizinto zokuhlekwa.
Ngokutsho kwegosa le-Workers' Party, iqela lakhe loorhulumente linoloyiko lokuba eli gama liza kuba nelithi "Twp" okanye "Pwp".
Ukuze sincede abafundi bethu baseWales, sifunda ukuba ngesiWelsh i-twp ithetha isitshixo, ize i-pwp ithethe i-poop.
