Isikhundla seKomiti yeNdlu yoWiso-mthetho ephetheyo ekuqulunqweni komthetho oyilwayo wokutshintsha igama sithi: Isigqibo sokugqibela malunga nezihloko zamalungu eNdlu yoWiso-mthetho ngokuqinisekileyo sisezandleni zabameli.
UMthetho ka-2017 woRhulumente waseWales wenza ukuba iNgqungquthela yaseWales itshintshe igama layo.
Kwiinyanga ezimbini ezidlulileyo, i-Eco-Lighthouse yazisa ingxelo yayo kwi-Intanethi.
Ngokuphathelele kwisibizo se-MPP, i-Commission ikhetha isibizo se-Welsh Parliament Member nesesifinyezo se-WMP, kodwa ke i-public consultation ikhethe ukunika i-MWP.
Abavoti bavelisa ezinye iindlela, kodwa ukufikelela kwisivumelwano kunzima, nto leyo ebangela ukuba intloko yeNdlu yoWiso-mthetho uElin Jones, azise umthetho oza kutshintsha igama lelizwe kwiiveki ezizayo.
UMthetho woHlaziyo uza kuchaphazela nezinye iinkalo zeNdlu yoWiso-mthetho, kuquka nokungabikho kwamalungu onyuliweyo kunye nokwakhiwa kweekomiti.
