Imvula eninzi emva kweNkanyamba uRosa, kwiingingqi ezisemazantsi-ntshona eUnited States
Njengoko kwakubonakalisiwe, iNkanyamba uRosa iza kuthamba njengoko iza kugqitha kumanzi abandayo kunxweme olusemantla eMexico.
Noko ke, kwiintsuku ezizayo, iRosa iza kuqhubeka ibangela izantyalantyala zemvula kwimimandla ekumantla eMexico nasemazantsi-ntshona eUnited States.
URosa, owayenomoya oshushu oziikhilomitha ezili-140 ngeyure, wafika njengenkanyamba ekuthiwa yiStorm, ngoLwesihlanu ekuseni, ngexesha lasempuma, malunga neekhilomitha ezingama-620 kumzantsi-ntshona wePunta Eugenia, eMexico.
Le nkanyamba kulindeleke ukuba ide ifike emantla ngeCawa.
NgoMvulo, njengoko iRosa isondela kwiPhondo laseKhalifoniya, iza kuba yiNkanyamba enkulu eza kugqobhoza kwintshona yeUnited States.
Le nkanyamba iza kunisa imvula emalunga nezentimitha eziyi-25 kwimimandla ethile yaseMexico ngoMvulo.
Emva koko, imvula evela kumoya osemoyeni iza kunisa imvula enkulu kumzantsi-ntshona welizwe.
Ukwehla kwemvula emandundu kangangeesentimitha ezintathu ukuya kwezilishumi kunokubangela izikhukula, izikhukula ezinemigodi, ukuguquka komhlaba entlango.
Isiphango esinzima somoya womoya sinokuzisa izantyalantyala zemvula eziziisentimitha ezi-5 ukuya kwezi-8 ngeyure kwiindawo ezithile, ingakumbi kwimimandla esezantsi yeNevada neArizona.
Kwinxalenye ethile yasemzantsi-ntshona kulindeleke ukuba kufike iimitha ezi-5 ukuya kwezi-10 zemvula, ingakumbi eArizona.
Iimpuphuma zisenokubakho, kodwa zidilike ngokukhawuleza ngenxa yemvula engaqhelekanga.
Xa izantyalantyala zemvula, akucetyiswa ukuba uhambe entlango.
Ngenxa yeemvula ezinamandla, imiwonyo inokuba yimilambo enogumbe, ize imifula ibe yimvula eneziqhwithi, yaye kwezinye iindawo, iba ngamafu amakhulu othuli.
Iinkanyamba eziphantsi zomoya eziza kubakho ziza kubangela izantyalantyala zemvula kwimimandla ekufutshane nonxweme lwaseMzantsi Kalifornia.
Kusenokubakho nemvula eziisentimitha ezisisi-1,5 ezinokubangela izikhukula ezincinane ezizele zizinto ezilahlekileyo kunye nemeko yomhlaba.
Le mvula iza kuba yeyokuqala ukuna kweli xesha lonyaka.
Imvula eshushu nezikhukula ziza kuqala ukubakho eArizona ngobusuku bangangeCawa nangentsasa yangoMvulo, zize zifikelele kwiindawo ezibanzi ngoMvulo emini nangeLwesibini.
Imvula enkulu iza kutsho kwingingqi yeZine Islands ngoLwesibini ize iqhubeke kude kube ngoLwesithathu.
Ngo-Oktobha, iqondo lobushushu liya kutshintsha kakhulu eUnited States, njengoko amaqondo obushushu eArctic ehla, kodwa amaqondo obushushu e-tropic aya kuhlala eshushu.
Oku kunokubangela umahluko omkhulu kubushushu obungaphantsi kweqondo lobushushu.
Umzekelo omhle woku ngoMgqibelo embindini weUnited States.
Iqondo lobushushu lahluka ngeqondo elingu-10 ngokukaCelsius ukusuka eKansas City, eMissouri, ukuya eOmaha, eNebraska, naseSt. Louis ukuya eDes Moines, eIowa.
Kwiintsuku ezimbalwa ezizayo, kusenokwenzeka ukuba ubushushu behlobo bube buninzi kwiindawo ezininzi.
Phakathi kwinyanga kaOktobha, amaqondo obushushu aphakathi kwama-25 ukuya kuma-30 ngokukaCelsius kwiindawo ezikumazantsi eGreat Plains ukuya kwiindawo ezithile kwiNtshona Koloni.
Amaqondo obushushu asezantsi aya kutsho kuma-25 kwiNew York ngoLwesibini, malunga nama-5 ngaphezulu kunesiqhelo.
Ngokutsho kwesibikezelo sezulu sexesha elide, amaqondo obushushu kwimpuma yeUnited States asenokuba ngaphezu kwamaqondo obushushu aphakathi de kube sekuqaleni kuka-Oktobha.
Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20 babukele uBrett Kavanaugh
Abantu abangaphezu kwezigidi ezingama-20 baye bakuphulaphula kumajelo kamabonwakude amathandathu oko kuthethwa ngumenzi wenkundla uBrett Kavanaugh kunye noChristine Blasey Ford, ibhinqa elathi ngo-1980 labeka ityala lokudlwengula.
Nangona kunjalo, le ngxaki yezopolitiko zange iphele, kwaza kwafuneka ukuba iinkqubo zikhe zibekho ngenxa yento eyenzeke ngomzuzu wokugqibela ngoLwesihlanu: ukuba uSen' u-Jeff Flake waseArizona, uye wakwazi ukuvumela i-FBI ukuba iphande ngezityholo ebezithethwe ngu-Jeff, iveki yonke.
Ford uxelele ikomiti yeenkundla zeli lizwe ukuba uqinisekile ukuba ngexesha lomsitho wesikolo esiphakamileyo uKavanaugh wamgxotha waza wazama ukumkhulula.
Kwingxelo yakhe ekrwada, uKavanaugh wathi wayeqinisekile ukuba oku akuzange kwenzeke.
La matyala, ngokutsho kweNielsen, abonwe ngabantu abazizigidi ezingama-20.4 ngoLwesihlanu.
I-Nielsen iqikelela umlinganiselo wababukeli be-CBS, i-ABC, i-NBC, i-CNN, i-Fox News Channel ne-MSNBC.
Amanani amanye amajelo asasaza le ntetho, afana nePBS, C-SPAN neFox Business Network, ayengekho kwangoko.
Kwakhona, iNielsen inengxaki yokulinganisa inani labantu ababukelayo kwiinkqubo zabo emsebenzini.
Ngokomzekelo, le mali ibalwa ngabantu ababukela imidlalo ekhatywayo okanye abadlala kwi-Oscar.
Ngokutsho kukaNielsen, phakathi kwazo zonke ezinye iziteshi, iFox News Channel, eyayixhasa iingcali ezazimela ukumiselwa kukaKavanaugh, yayibeneyona mpapasho iphakamileyo, yayinababukeli abazizigidi ezi-5.69 ngosuku.
I-ABC yeyesibini ngamanqaku ayizigidi ezi-3.26.
I-CBS yayifikelelwa ngabantu abayi-3.1, i-NBC yayifikelelwa ngabantu abayi-2.94, i-MSNBC yayifikelelwa ngabantu abayi-2.89, i-CNN yayifikelelwa ngabantu abayi-2.52 ezigidi, ngokwengxelo yeNielsen.
Umdla awuzange uphele nasemva kokuba ndigqibile ukuva.
Umdlali ophambili kwidrama yangoLwesihlanu yayinguSenator Flake.
Emva kokuba igosa lesigqeba elilawulayo leRiphabliki likhuphe ingxelo yokuba liza kuvota kuSenator Kavanaugh, ngoLwesihlanu kusasa, u-CNN noCBS, babukele inkitha yabaqhankqalazi njengoko wayekhwela kwiinqwelo-mafutha eziya kwiKomiti yeNkundla.
Wayengakwazi ukujonga, njengoko wayejongwa ngabantu, abe CNN bebesasaza loo mboniso.
"Ndim lo phambi kwenu", yatsho le nkosikazi kwiSenate.
