Kwiintsuku nje ezimbalwa emva koko, amajelo eendaba neenkqubo zekhebula zaye zabukela abahlali bevota phambi kwebhunga lesigqeba elilawulayo ukuze liqinisekise ukuba ukhetho lukaKavanaugh luza kuvunywa liBhunga leNgwevu liphela.
Noko ke, uFlake wathi wayeza kuyenza loo nto kuphela ukuba iFBI iphinda ikhangele izityholo zenkundla zenkundla ezibekwe ngumgqatswa kwiveki ezayo, njengoko iDemocrats eyayikwintla yabemi baseDemocratic yayibongoza.
UFlake waqonda ukuba oku kuyimfuneko emva kokuthetha nomhlobo wakhe, uSenator Chris Coons ongumDemocratic.
