Amakhulu Abulawa KwiTsunami Ebangelwe Yinyikima EIndonesia, Inani Labaswelekileyo Linyuka
Abantu abaninzi baye bagutyungelwa ngamanzi, kwaza kwafa abantu abangama-384 xa amaza amakhulu afikelela kunxweme lwelizwe ngenxa yenyikima enkulu kunye nezikhukula kwisiqithi saseIndonesia iSulawesi, kutsho amagosa aseburhulumenteni ngoMgqibelo.
Amakhulu abantu ayehlanganisene kwisixeko sasePalu kumsitho owawungoLwesihlanu, xa amaza aziimitha ezisibhozo ukuphakama afika elunxwemeni ngentsasa yangorha, agubungela abantu abaninzi, etshabalalisa yonke into eyayiphambi kwawo.
Le ntlekele ibangelwe yinyikima enkulu ebingu-7.5 ngamandla.
Xa izikhukula zaqhambuka izolo, abantu baye bahlala elunxwemeni, abazange babaleke ngoko nangoko, baza babulawa zizikhukula,  utshilo uSutopo Purwo Nugroho, isithethi se-Indonesian Disaster Relief Agency (BNPB) kwinkomfa yeendaba eJakarta.
Utsunami akazange afike nje, watsala iimoto, iintonga, izindlu nayo yonke into eselunxwemeni Utshilo u-Nugroho, wongezelela ukuba itsunami yayibaleka ngesantya se-800km/h elwandle ngaphambi kokuba ifikelele elunxwemeni.
Abanye baye bakhwela emithini baza basinda kuloo mkhukula, watsho.
Abantu abamalunga ne-16 700 baye bafudukela kwiindawo ezikhuselekileyo eziyi-24 ezisePhulia.
Iifoto zeenqwelo-moya ze-AFP ezibonisa lo monakalo zibonisa izakhiwo ezininzi ezidilikileyo, iibhuloho eziwileyo, kunye nemosque.
NgoMgqibelo, iidolophu eziselunxwemeni zafikelwa ziinyikima.
Iinyikima zazinokuviwa kwindawo enabantu abamalunga nezigidi ezi-2.4 abahlala kuyo.
Ngokutsho kweArhente YaseIndonesia Ephonononga NgobuGcisa (iBPPT), inyikima yangoLwesihlanu yakhupha amandla aphindwe ka-200 kwalawo avela kwibhombu yeathom eyadutyulwa kwiHiroshima kwiMfazwe Yehlabathi II.
Le nkampani yalek' umsundulu isithi, ngenxa yokuba le dolophu ikumda wetheku elide, iziganeko ezenzeka apho zisenokuba zabangela ukuba kubekho inkanyamba.
UNugroho uthi umonakalo owenzekileyo ubukhulu becala, kuba amawakawaka amakhaya atshabalala, izibhedlele, iivenkile ezinkulu neehotele zatshabalala.
Uthe izidumbu zabantu abaliqela zifunyenwe kumabhodlo ezakhiwo, kwaye sele kukho abantu abangama-540 abalimalayo, kunye nabanye abangama-29 abafunwayo.
Ngokutsho kukaNugroho, abantu abafayo nabonzakeleyo kule ndawo ibizwa ngokuba yiDonggala, ekufutshane nePalu, ekumgama oziikhilomitha ezingama-300 ukusuka kwindawo eyayitshayelwe yinyikima, banokuba baninzi ngakumbi.
UNugroho uthi, "Iinkqubo zonxibelelwano zivaliwe ngokupheleleyo, akukho ndlela yakwazi ukufumana inkcazelo ngoDonggala".
'Bangaphezu kwama-300 000 abantu abahlala apho,' itsho njalo iRed Cross, ekwachaza ukuba iingcali zayo kunye namavolontiya sele besendleleni eya kuloo ndawo intlithwe yintlekele.
Imeko sele imbi, kodwa isenokuba mbi nangakumbi.
NgoMgqibelo, i-Arhente yezokhuseleko yafumana izityholo ezininzi ngenxa yokungaxeleli abantu ngesaqhwithi esihlasela iPalu, kodwa abaphathi bathi amaza sele efikile elunxwemeni ngexesha kwakusenziwa isilumkiso.
Omnye umboniso owaba kwiiwebhsayithi zoluntu ubonisa indoda ikhwaza isitsho kubantu abaphambukayo ukuba kuza kubakho isaqhwithi.
Kwiimizuzu nje embalwa, kwaphuma amanzi amaninzi, arhuqela iinqwelo-mafutha nezakhiwo.
