Oku akuthethanga emva kokuba urhulumente wase-US enze izibhengezo malunga nobukrelekrele bokusebenza, nangona i-US ingenayo isicwangciso-qhinga se-AI.
Ngelo xesha, iChina nayo yabhengeza izicwangciso zayo ezihambelana noku: injongo yayo yokuba ngowama-2030 ibe lilizwe lokuqala ehlabathini lonke ekuphuhliseni i-AI.
Ukutyhubela kabini umlinganiselo weendleko zophando lwe-AI bekuya kuba sisiqalo esifanelekileyo, kuba onke amanye amazwe ashiyeke emva kakhulu kunase-US, kwaye ukuphumelela kwe-AI kusemnyango  utshilo uLee.
Xa ephindaphinda kabini imali ayibekela uphando, usenokuphinda kabini amathuba okuba iUnited States ibe lelona lizwe liza kuba liphambili kubuchule bokwenza izinto, utshilo xa wayencokola neCNBC.
Lee, onencwadi ethi AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order, ekhutshwe kule nyanga nguHoughton Mifflin Harcourt, ongusomphathiswa omkhulu weSinovation Ventures, inkampani ethe yatyala imali kwiFace++ enye yeenkampani eziphambili ze-AI eChina.
Ngeminyaka yee-1980 wayesebenza kwiYunivesithi yaseCarnegie Mellon, apho wasebenza khona kwi-AI eyaphumelelayo ukubetha oyena mdlali ubalaseleyo waseMelika u-Othello, kwaye kamva waba lilungu lekomiti yeMicrosoft Research, kwaye kamva waba ngumongameli we-Google China.
ULee wavuma ukuba uBukumkani buye baphumelela kwiikhompethi zobugcisa eziye zaqhutywa ngurhulumente, kuquka neDARPA Robotics Challenge, waza wabuza ukuba baza kuqhuba nini na ezinye iikhompethi ze-Robotics, kuba xa kunjalo kuza kubakho ithuba lokufuna abantu abaya kwenza izinto eziza kwenzeka kwikamva.
Lo kaLee uthi, oososayensi baseUnited States badla ngokuzama ukufumana imali karhulumente ukuze benze uphando.
Ayingobantu baseTshayina abaqhawula iintloko kwicandelo lezenzululwazi, kodwa ziinkampani ezinkulu.
