Kulo nyaka, iSebe lezoKhuselo laseMerika lamisela iZiko eliDibeneyo lobuGcisa boBugcisa (iJoint Artificial Intelligence Center) apho iingcali zamashishini kunye nezifundiswa zinokusebenza kunye, kwaye iNdlu ye-White House yabhengeza ukusekwa kweKomiti yoKhetho kwiBugcisa boBugcisa (Select Committee on Artificial Intelligence).
