IMacedonia iza kuba neereferendum yokutshintsha igama lelizwe
Abantu baseMakedoni bavotele ukutshintsha igama lelizwe kwiRiphabhlikhi yaseNyakatho yeMakedoni ngeCawe, besenza isigqibo sokususa ingxabano neGrisi kangangamashumi eminyaka, eyayithintele ukwamkelwa kwebango lelizwe lokungena kwi-EU nakwi-NATO.
IGrisi, enye yephondo layo ibizwa ngokuba yiMacedonia, iye yathi igama lommelwane wayo wasentla libonisa ukuba inyanzelisa ummandla waseGrisi onegama elifanayo, ngoko ke iye yakhetha ukungayithethi le nto, ukuza kuthi ga ngoku, kwiinkqubo zayo ze-EU nezaseNATO.
NgoJuni oorhulumente ababini bafikelela kwisivumelwano sokutshintsha igama likaRhulumente, kodwa abachasi beemvakalelo zobuzwe bathi ukutshintsha igama kuya kubeka umda kwiimpawu zobuhlanga zabantu baseMacedonia, abaninzi babo abangamaSlav.
UMongameli Gjorge Ivanov uxele ukuba akayi kuthatha inxaxheba kwireferendum, kwaye ngenxa yephulo lokuyixotha, unokuthandabuza ukuba uya kuba nakho ukufikelela kwi-50% yenani labantu abafunekayo ukuze i-referendum ibe yinyani.
Umbuzo okwiphepha lokuvota uthi: "Ngaba uyayixhasa into yokuba eli lizwe libe lilungu leNATO ne-EU, yaye ngaba uyavumelana nesivumelwano esenziwe neGrisi?"
Abo bathethelela ukuguqulwa kwegama, bekhokelwa nguNkulumbuso uZoran Zaev, bathi eli lixabiso elifanele ukuhlawulwa ukuze iMacedonia, enye yamazwe aphuma kumathambo eYugoslavia, ibe nethuba lokuba ngamalungu e-EU ne-NATO.
'Ndize apha namhlanje ukuza kuvota ngekamva lelizwe, ukuze ulutsha lwaseMacedonia luphile ngokukhululekileyo phantsi kokhuselo lwe-European Union, kuba oko kuthetha ubomi obukhuselekileyo kuthi sonke,' utshilo uOlivera Georgijevska (79) eSkopje.
Nangona iRefendum ngokwayo inganyanzelekanga ngokwasemthethweni, amalungu ePalamente amaninzi aye avakalisa ukuba azibophelele kwiziphumo zayo.
Ukuze kutshintshwe igama, kufuneka isibini esithathwini sentshaba ephalamende.
Ngokutsho kweKomiti yeeLwimi zelizwe, akukho zibhengezo zolwaphulo-mthetho ezifunyenweyo kude kube ngo-1:00 emva kwemini.
Kodwa ukuza kuthi ga ngoku, inqanaba lokuya kuvota belifikelela kwi-16% kuphela, emva kwe-34% kunyulo luka-2016 (apho i-66% yabemi ababhalisiweyo bavota).
'Ndize kuvota ngenxa yabantwana bam, kuba sinendawo eYurophu,' utshilo uGjos Tanevski, 62, owayevota eSkopje, ikomkhulu.
Inkulumbuso yaseStrumitsa, uZoran Zaev, umfazi wakhe uZorica nonyana wakhe uDushko, bavotele ukutshintsha igama lelizwe kwiRiphabliki kaSeptemba 30, 2018 ukuze libe yinxalenye ye-EU ne-NATO.
KwiSkopje, phambi kwezakhiwo zePalamente, uVladimir Kavardarkov (54) wamisa iqonga elincinane kunye nezitulo neentente ukuze bamamele abo babeza kuvala iRefendum.
Sikwaxhasa ubulungu belizwe kwi-NATO nakwi-EU, kodwa sifuna ukujoyina ngeqhayiya, ngentloko ephakanyisiweyo, hayi ngomnyango omnyama,  utshilo uKavadarkov.
 Nangona singamahlwempu, asilahlekwanga sisidima sethu.
Ukuba asifuni kwamkelwa njengeMakedoni, sinokuya eChina okanye eRashiya njengenxalenye yokudityaniswa kwe-Eurasia.
Ngokutsho kukaNobhala oyiNtloko uZaev, ukuba lilungu leNATO kunokuzisa utyalo-mali eMakedoni, oludinga kakhulu kwilizwe elinabantu abangaphangeliyo abangaphezu kwama-20%.
Ndiyathemba ukuba uninzi lwabantu luza kusixhasa, kuba ngaphezu kwe-80% yabantu beli lizwe baxhasa ubulungu be-EU ne-NATO utshilo uZaev emva kokuvota kwakhe.
Uthe ukuvota kuka-Ngqika kuthetha ukuqinisekisa ikamva lelizwe.
Ngokutsho kophando olwenziwe yiZiko laseMacedonia loPhando ngezePolitiko, ngoMvulo, kuqikelelwa ukuba i-30% ukuya kwi-43% yabemi baseMacedonia baza kuya kuvota, nto leyo engeyiyo inqanaba elifunekayo.
