John Edward: Ulwimi lubalulekile ukuze ube ngummi wehlabathi
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseScotland zisoloko zinemfundo ebalaseleyo. Xa sijonga iziphumo ezibalaseleyo zeemviwo, le meko ayizange itshintshe ngo-2018, iqiniswe yimpumelelo yomntu ngamnye neqela kwezemidlalo, kwezobugcisa, umculo nakwezinye izinto ezenziwa luluntu.
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseScotland, ezibizwa ngokuba yiThe Scottish Council of Independent Schools (SCIS), zinezifundo ezingaphezu kwama-30 000 yaye zizimisele ukubonelela ngeyona nkonzo ibalaseleyo kubafundi nakubazali.
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zizama ukuxhobisa abafundi ukuze baqhubeke befunda, bafumane imfundo ephakamileyo, babe nemisebenzi abayithandayo baze babe ngabemi behlabathi.
Kwicandelo lemfundo apho kukho ithuba lokuyila nokuphumeza izifundo zesikolo ezenzelwe wena, sibona ukuba iilwimi zanamhlanje ziyaqhubeka nokuduma kwaye zifunwa.
UNelson Mandela wathi: "Ukuba uthetha nomntu ngolwimi alwaziyo, luya kuyifikelela intloko".
Kodwa xa uthetha ngolwimi lwakhe, oko kuya kufikelela intliziyo yakhe.
Esi sisikhumbuzo esibalulekileyo, kuba asinakuthembela kwisiNgesi kuphela xa sifuna ukwakha ubuhlobo nentembelo nabantu abavela kwamanye amazwe.
Ngokutsho kweziphumo zovavanyo zalo nyaka, abafundi abakwizikolo ezizimeleyo kulo lonke eli lizwe bafumana ezona ziphumo ziphezulu kwiilwimi zasemzini.
Abafundi abangama-68 ekhulwini kubo bonke abafundi beelwimi zasemzini bafumana amanqaku aphezulu (ama-85 ekhulwini).
Kwisikolo seSCIS esinabafundi abangama-74 kuphela, abafundi abangama-72 ekhulwini bafumana amanqaku aphezulu kwisiTsonga, ngoxa abangama-72 ekhulwini kwabafunda isiJamani, abangama-69 ekhulwini kwabafunda isiFrentshi, abangama-63 ekhulwini kwabo bafunda isiSpanish bafumana amanqaku aphezulu.
Ezi ziphumo zikwaxhasa ukuba izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseScotland zijonga iilwimi zasemzini njengento ebalulekileyo ekufuneka abantwana nolutsha bayazi kwikamva.
Namhlanje, iilwimi njengezifundo ezikhethiweyo zibaluleke ngokulinganayo nenzululwazi, iteknoloji, inzululwazi yezobugcisa kunye nemathematika, kuzo zombini izikolo ezizimeleyo nakwezinye.
Uphando olwenziwe ngo-2014 yiKomiti yeMfundo noQeqesho yaseUnited Kingdom lubonisa ukuba i-17 pesenti yabaqeshi ithi ukungabi nalwazi ngeelwimi kwenza kube nzima ukuzalisa izithuba.
Oku kubonisa ukuba ukwazi ulwimi kuya kusiba yimfuneko ukuze ulutsha lube nempumelelo kumsebenzi walo.
Ekubeni abantu abaninzi befuna ukwazi iilwimi zasemzini kwiindawo zabo zempangelo, ukwazi ulwimi kubalulekile kweli hlabathi lihlanganiswe luhlabathi.
Enoba umntu ukhetha ntoni na ebomini, ukufunda ulwimi olutsha kunokumenza abe nolwazi oluhlala luhleli nolunomvuzo.
Ukukwazi kwakhe ukunxibelelana ngqo nabantu bezinye iintlanga kunika ithuba lokuba abe ngumncintiswano kubaviwa abathetha iilwimi ezininzi.
Uhlolisiso olwenziwe nguYouGov kubantu abadala abangama-4 000 eUnited Kingdom ngo-2013 lubonisa ukuba i-75 ekhulwini yabantu abaphendulweyo abakwazi ukuthetha kakuhle iilwimi zasemzini ukuze bakwazi ukuncokola nabanye abantu, yaye isiFrentshi kuphela kolwimi oluthethwa ngabantu abangaphezu kwe-10 ekhulwini (15%).
Ngoko ke, kubalulekile ukuba sinikele ingqalelo ekufundiseni abantwana bethu ulwimi.
Ukwazi iilwimi ezininzi, ingakumbi ezo zeentlanga ezikhulayo, kunokubanceda abantwana bakwazi ukuzenzela izinto eziza kubanceda babe nemisebenzi ebalulekileyo xa bebadala.
ESkotlani, izikolo ziza kuba neelwimi ezahlukahlukeneyo.
Uninzi lwezikolo luza kugxininisa kwiilwimi zakudala, ngoxa ezinye ziza kufundisa iilwimi ezinjengesiMandarin okanye isiJapanese, eziza kuba zezona zibalulekileyo e-UK ngo-2020.
Kungakhathaliseki ukuba yintoni umntwana wakho ayithandayo, uya kukwazi ukufunda iilwimi ezininzi ezikhethiweyo kwizikolo ezizimeleyo, uqeqeshwa ngabafundisi-ntsapho abaziingcali kwezo lwimi.
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zaseScotland zizimisele ukubonelela abantwana ngeendawo zokufunda eziza kubanceda bakwazi ukuphumelela nokuba sekumnyam' entla.
Kulula ukubona ukuba kule meko yehlabathi apho iilwimi zisengundoqo kwikamva lelizwe, kwaye kufuneka oko kuboniswe kwimfundo.
Enyanisweni, ukwazi iilwimi zale mihla kufanele kujongwe njengobuchule bokunxibelelana namazwe ngamazwe.
Izikolo ezizimeleyo zinika ulutsha lwaseSkotlani ukhetho, iinketho kunye nemfundo esemgangathweni.
