Ukumisela ukuba iNyakatho Korea iyeke ukuzimela yodwa ukuba ayithembanga kwiqabane layo
UMphathiswa Wezangaphandle waseMntla Korea uxelele iUN ngoMgqibelo ukuba ukuqhubeka kwezohlwayo kuye kwabangela ukuba iUnited States ingathenjwa, yaye akukho ndlela yokuba ilizwe layo linikezele ngezixhobo zenyukliya.
KwiNtlanganiso Yonyaka Yombutho Wehlabathi, uRi Jongho wathi iNorth Korea iye "yazithabathela amanyathelo abalulekileyo nabonisa ubuchule" ebudeni bonyaka ophelileyo, njengokuyeka ukuvavanywa kwenyukliya nemipu yayo, ukuvala indawo yokuvavanya inyukliya, nokuthembisa ukungayandisi izixhobo zayo zenyukliya nokusebenzisa iteknoloji yayo yenyukliya.
"Ngelishwa, asiyiboni impendulo efanayo evela kumaMerika", watsho.
 Ngenxa yokungabi nalukholo eMelika, sivakalelwa kukuba ukhuseleko lwelizwe lethu alukho mthethweni, yaye phantsi kweemeko ezinjalo, asinakukwazi ukuyekisa unilaterally.
Nangona uRi ephinde wavakalisa ukuphoxeka kweNyakatho Korea ngokuchaswa kweWashington kwingcinga yokuyeka ukutshabalalisa inyukliya ngokwamacandelo, apho iNtshona Korea yayiza kufumana imivuzo ngenyathelo elilandelayo, intetho yakhe yabonakala inentsingiselo kuba akazange ayichase ngokucacileyo into yokuba yenziwe ngenyukliya ngokwamacandelo, njengoko iPhangean yenzile ukuza kuthi ga ngoku.
U-Ri ubhekisa kwingxelo eyenziwa nguKim Jong Un noDonald Trump kwindibano yokuqala phakathi komongameli waseMerika osebenzayo kunye nomlawuli waseMntla Korea eyayiseSingapore ngoJuni 12, apho uKim wathembisa ukuba uza kusebenza ukuze iKorea ingabi nayo inqwelo-mkhosi yenyukliya, ngoxa uTrump wayeqinisekisa ukuba iNyakatho ikhuselekile.
INorth Korea ifuna ukuvala imfazwe yaseKorea eyaqala ngowe-1950 ukusa kowe-1953. Kodwa iUnited States ithi ifanele ivele kuqala ukuze iphele imfazwe yeathom.
IWashington ayizange ivumele neyona ndlela inzima yezizwe ngezizwe zokungenelela kwiNorth Korea.
"I-US iyanyanzelisa ukuba siqalise ngokuyeka ukufaka izixhobo zenyukliya kwaye izimisele ukusifaka uxinzelelo ngezisongelo ukuze inyanzelise ukuthanda kwayo, kwaye iyaphikisana nokuba ngubani na onokuthi aphumelele emfazweni", utshilo u-Ri.
 Ingcamango yokuba izohlwayo zinokusenza sidlale ngathi siyatshaya, yinto nje abantu abangasaziyo abayithandayo.
Ingxaki kukuba, izohlwayo ezingacothanga ziza kusenza sibe noxanduva olungakumbi.
U-Ri akazange akhankanye ukuba intlanganiso yesibini phakathi kuka-Kim no-Trump icwangcisiwe, nangona kunjalo, umongameli wase-US ukhankanye ngokukodwa kwi-UN ekuqaleni kweveki.
Lo mphathiswa ukhankanye iintlanganiso ezintathu phakathi kukaKim noMongameli waseMzantsi Korea uMun Jae-in kwiinyanga ezintlanu ezidlulileyo, wongezelela ngelithi, "Ukuba ilizwe elibhekiswe ekuthini liyekise izixhobo zenyukliya yiMzantsi Korea, hayi iUnited States, ukuyekiswa kwezixhobo zenyukliya kwisiqithi saseKorea bekungayi kuba yimeko engekho ngqiqweni".
Nangona kunjalo, i-tone ka-Ri kwi-speech yakhe yahluke kakhulu kunyaka ophelileyo xa wayexelela i-UN General Assembly ukuba ukujolisa kwi-continent yaseMntla Melika nge-missile yaseMntla Korea ayinakuphepheka emva kokuba uTrump, uMongameli ongendawo, ebiza u-Kim njengomntu we-rocket, ozimisele ukuzimela.
Kwiintlanganiso zeZizwe Ezimanyeneyo zonyaka, uTrump, owathi kunyaka ophelileyo wasongela ngokutshabalalisa uMntla Korea, wamncoma uKim ngokwenza kwakhe amanyathelo okuyekisa izixhobo kodwa wathi kusekho umsebenzi omninzi ekufuneka wenziwe kwaye izohlwayo ziya kuhlala zikhona de uMntla Korea uphumelele kumsebenzi wokuncitshiswa kwezikhali zenyukliya.
NgoLwesithathu uTrump wathi akukho xesha limiselweyo, ngoko nokuba kungathabatha iminyaka emibini, iminyaka emithathu okanye iinyanga ezintlanu, akunamsebenzi.
