Abafundi baseHarvard bafundiswa ukuphumla ngokwaneleyo
Isifundo esitsha saseHarvard saqala kunyaka ophelileyo, safundisa abafundi ukuba balale ixesha elide, ukuze balwe nenkcubeko yokulala ubusuku bonke, eyandiswe yicaffeine.
Esinye isazi sifikelele kwisigqibo sokuba abafundi abafunda kwiiyunivesithi eziphambili ehlabathini badla ngokungazi nokuba bafanele bazikhathalele njani.
Le khosi, ekuthiwa yeyokuqala ngqa ukubakho kweli lizwe, yayicetywe nguNjingalwazi Charles Czeisler, ofundisa unyango lokulala kwiHarvard Medical School nongugqirha wezifo zengqondo kwiBrigham and Women's Hospital.
Into eyamenza wacinga ngale khosi kukuba wayethethe ngomphumo wokungalali kakuhle ekufundeni.
Ekugqibeleni, intombazana ethile yeza kum yaza yathi: Kutheni ndijamelene nale nto kuphela ngoku, njengomntu ophumelele?
Uthi akazange axelelwe ngokubaluleka kokulala, nto leyo eyamothusayo, njengoko wayexelela iThe Telegraph.
Kwisifundo esikhuthazwayo esiqala kulo nyaka, abafundi bafundiswa ukuba indlela abalala ngayo ibalulekile ukuze baphumelele esikolweni nasemidlalweni, ngaphezu kokuba nempembelelo entle kwimpilo yabo.
Ngokutsho kukaPaul Barreira, ongunjingalwazi wezifo zengqondo kwisikolo sezamayeza saseHarvard, nomlawuli wenkonzo yezempilo, le yunivesithi yagqiba ekubeni iqalise le klasi ngenxa yokuba abafundi babelala kakhulu ebudeni beveki.
Le klasi iyure enye inemisebenzi emininzi enxibelelanayo.
Ngokomzekelo, omnye umboniso ubonisa iklasi eklasini apho abafundi banokukrwaqula iikomityi zekofu, amakhethini, izihlangu zokujima neencwadi ukuze bafunde ngemiphumo yecaffeine nokukhanya, indlela ukungalali kakuhle okuyichaphazela ngayo indlela abadlala ngayo nokungqubana kwezinto xa belele.
Kwelinye icala, abantu bafundiswa ukuba xa bengakwazi ukulala ngokwaneleyo, banokuba sesichengeni sokwenzakala sisifo sentliziyo, isisu esibuhlungu, uxinezeleko nomhlaza.
Iinkqubo zentsimi ziquka ukubonisa imaphu yephondo leekholeji enemifanekiso enemifanekiso ukuze abafundi bacinge ngezinto abazenzayo suku ngalunye.
Siyazi ukuba asiyi kuyitshintsha indlela abafundi abaziphatha ngayo ngoko nangoko.
Kodwa sicinga ukuba banelungelo lokufumana olu lwazi kanye njengokuba benelungelo lokufumana ulwazi ngemiphumo yokutshaya empilweni yabo", utsho njalo uNjingalwazi uCheisler.
Uthi, "kuye kwaqhubeka kukho inkcubeko yokuba ukufunda ubusuku bonke kuyeyona nto iphambili", yaye uthi ubugcisa bale mihla nengcinezelo yabafundi zibangela ukuba ukungalali kubangele iingxaki ezingakumbi.
Ukulala ngokwaneleyo nokumgangatho ophezulu kuyeyona nto abafundi bayisebenzisayo ukuze balwe noxinezeleko, ukudandatheka, ixhala kwanokuxinezeleka, kuba ukungalali ngokwaneleyo kubangela ukuba ingqondo ibe yindlala, nto leyo ebangela ukuba umntu azive elambile.
URaymond So wancedisa ukuyila izifundo zikaNjingalwazi uCzeisler, umfundi waseCalifornia oneminyaka eli-19 ubudala ofunda i-chemistry ne-biophysics, yaye kunyaka ophelileyo waba ngowokuqala ukufundiswa izifundo zikaNjingalwazi uCzeisler eHarvard.
Wathi abo babephulaphule bamenza waqonda ukuba umele aqale afumane imfundo yasesikolweni.
Ithemba ukuba njengenyathelo elilandelayo, abafundi abagqibeleleyo baya kuba nako ukuthatha inxaxheba kwinkqubo yoqeqesho efanayo ngaphambi kokuba bafikelele kwicandelo lokukhuphisana.
UProfesa Czeisler ucebisa ukuba abafundi babeke ii-alarm xa befuna ukuya kulala, ii-alarm xa befuna ukuvuka, baze bazi ukuba ukukhanya okukhutshwe zizikrini zombane nezibane ezivelisa ukukhanya okuluhlaza okwesibhakabhaka kunokubenza bangakwazi ukuzibamba baze bangakwazi ukulala.
