Ngoku sele kuyinto eqhelekileyo ukukhangela iimbekiselo zeBrexit kuyo yonke imiboniso bhanyabhanya yaseBritani, kwaye akukho nto ingaphaya kwe-franchise ebizwa ngokuba yiJohnny English, ekumgangatho we-action comedy/parody, inxalenye yayo yokuqala, uJohnny English ngo-2003, kwaye inxalenye yesibini, uJohnny English Reloaded, yafika kwi-cinema ngo-2011.
Ngaba iBritani iza kuthumela kwelinye ilizwe iincwadi ezibonisa indlela abantu abazenza ngayo izinto?
Ngokuqinisekileyo, lo mfo ukhohlakeleyo, ongenamqolo, nongakwaziyo ukuzenzela nto uJohnny English wayenezinto eziza kumenza abuye. Igama lakhe libonisa ukuba lo mfo usengumntu nje ofanayo, wayedalwe ukuze abantu ababukelayo kwimifanekiso eshukumayo kumazwe athetha iilwimi ezingezizo ezesiNgesi, bakwazi ukuhleka ngaye.
UJohnny English, ngokuqinisekileyo, ngumsebenzi ofihlakeleyo oyimfihlo, onobuchule bokuzenza umntu othandwayo, ngoko ke ukhumbuza kancinane uMphathi weKlouseau, ngamanye amaxesha uMnu. Bean, kwaye ngamanye amaxesha umfana owenza umboniso womculo weMotowners, ingoma ephambili yomsitho weOlimpiki zaseLondon ngo-2012.
Umlinganiswa wokuqala ukwasekelwa kumntu owayenomdla wokuthatha uhambo oluya kumazwe ngamazwe, owayedlalwe nguAtkinson, kwi-TV yeBarclaycard eyayisele ilibalekile, kwaye washiya umbhodamo kuyo yonke indawo.
Kukho izinto ezimbalwa ezintle kwifilimu yakutshanje kaJohnny English.
Ndayithanda indlela uJohnny English, enxibe iimpahla zamandulo, awayesondela ngayo kwihelikopta, xa efika, imijikelezo yayibetha ngesiqalo sakhe kangangexeshana.
I-Atkinson's comic vein isebenza kakuhle kwifilimu, kodwa ihlazo lefilimu aliyi kusebenza kakuhle, kwaye libonakala liyimfuneko, kuba namhlanje ii-franchise ezinomdla njengeefilimu zikaJames Bond okanye iMishini ye-Impossible zifikelela kwi-comic.
Ukuziva ngathi amahla-ndinyuka aloo bhanya-bhanya ajoliswe kubantwana, kum, ibali likaJohnny English elinencasa, elingenamsebenzi alifikeleli kumgangatho wobulumko nobuchule obuboniswa nguAtkinson kwimizuzu yakhe engathethiyo kuMnu. Bean.
Inyaniso ehlala ihleli yile: IBritani isengozini enkulu.
Igquba le-cybercriminal liye laqhekeza kwi-network ye-super-secret ye-British Intelligence, kwaye lachaza bonke abasebenzi baseBritani, kwaye eyona nto ibangele inkxalabo enkulu kumsebenzi we-agent, uKevin Eldon, onetyala, kodwa unetyala elincinci kakhulu kwifilimu.
Le isenokuba yeyona nto ibalulekileyo kwibhokisi kaNkulumbuso ekrwada neyahlukileyo, nowayengengathandwa kwiipolitiki, u-Emma Thompson udlala uThereza May, kwaye wenza konke okusemandleni akhe ukuze abonakalise lo mlinganiswa wakhe ubhalwe kakubi.
Abacebisi bakhe bezobuntlola bathi ekubeni bonke oonozakuzaku beye babhencwa, kufuneka athumele omnye umakad' enetha.
Eli gosa lithanjisiweyo ngokuqinisekileyo lifana noJohnny English, owathi emva kokuphelelwa ngumsebenzi wasebenza kwisikolo esiphakamileyo, kodwa ngoku ufundisa abantwana ukuba babe ngoonogada.
U-English uthuthwa ngokukhawuleza aye e-Whitehall, apho adibana khona ne-Bough, owayengumgcini wakhe owayengumgcini-mpu, owayedlala indima kaBen Miller, kwindibano yocweyo.
