Kwiveki ezayo, i-Global Citizen Festival, eza kube isandul' ukuqhutywa, kulindeleke ukuba ithathe indawo enkulu yaseCentral Park, apho kuya kubakho abantu abangayi kumamela nje kuphela iintetho zikaJanet Jackson, uCardi B okanye uShawn Mendes, kodwa baya kukwazisa ngeyona njongo iphambili yalo mbhiyozo: ukuphelisa ubuhlwempu obungqongqo ngowama-2030.
I-Global Citizen Festival yaqala ngo-2012 njengenxalenye yeprojekthi ye-Global Poverty, eqhutywa liqela lomgaqo-nkqubo wamazwe ngamazwe, ejolise ekupheliseni ubuhlwempu ngokubandakanya abantu abaninzi kumlo ochaphazelekayo wokulwa nobuhlwempu.
Abantu abanokufumana itikiti elihlawulelwayo lekontshi (ngaphandle kokuba bazimisele ukuhlawula itikiti leVIP) abanokuzibandakanya kwimisebenzi ethile okanye benze izinto ezithile, njengokuvolontiya, ukuthumela i-imeyile kwiinkokeli zezopolitiko, umnxeba, okanye enye into enokubenza bagxininise injongo yeprojekthi yokuphelisa ubuhlwempu.
Kodwa ke, kule minyaka ili-12 idluleyo, ngaba iGlobal Citizen iye yaziphumeza iinjongo zayo?
Ngaba ukupha abantu amatikiti ekhonsathi yindlela eluncedo yokunyanzela abanye ukuba benze into, okanye ngaba yindlela entsha yokuxhakamfula abantu xa beziva ngathi benze into ebalulekileyo ngokusayina isicelo esiku-intanethi okanye bathumele i-tweet?
Ukususela ngo-2011, ngokutsho kweGlobal Citizen, kukho ngaphezu kwe-19 yezigidi zezenzo ezenziwe ngabaxhasi beprojekthi, ezilungiselelwe iinjongo ezininzi ezahlukeneyo.
