NgoLwesithathu, uMongameli Donald Trump wase-United States, wathetha ngesibhengezo sakhe esikwincwadi yeendaba ethengisa kakhulu eIowa, i-China Daily Des Moines Register, esithi i-China izama ukuphazamisa unyulo lwase-United States oluzayo ngoNovemba 6.
Izityholo zikaTrump zokuba iPeking izama ukuphazamisa unyulo lwaseMelika, ezinye izikhulu zaseMelika eziye zaxelela iReuters, zibonisa ukuba iWashington iyaqhubeka nokunyusa inkqubela yayo yokulwa neChina, ngenjongo yokuzama ukuyityhafisa.
Nangona kuqhelekile ukuba oorhulumente bamanye amazwe bakhuthaze urhwebo namazwe abo ngeentengiso, iBeijing neWashington basoloko besilwa imfazwe yorhwebo, behlawulisa izinto ezithengiswa kwamanye amazwe.
Iingcali zaseMelika nezaseTshayina zithi, ekuqaleni kwemfazwe yorhwebo, amaTshayina aye ajolisa ekuthini ahlasele abathengisi kumazwe apho uTrump neRepublican Party baziwa khona, kuquka neIowa.
UTerry Branstad, onguNobhala weSebe laseMerika eChina nowayesakuba nguRhuluneli waseIowa, uthi iPeking iye yabangela ingozi kubasebenzi, amafama namashishini aseMerika, kuba iIowa ithumela izinto zayo ezininzi zaseChina.
U-Branstad wabhala kwinqaku lakhe lezimvo kwiDes Moines Register ngeCawa wathi "i-China iyaqhubeka nokonakalisa ilizwe lethu ngokufaka iintengiso zentengiso kwi-Press yethu yasimahla".
"Urhulumente waseTshayina usebenzisa kakubi isithethe saseMerika esihlonelwayo senkululeko yokuthetha nokuthetha xa esasaza intetho yakhe kwiphephandaba iDes Moines Register, ekhokhelwa ukuba ihlawule iintengiso"
 Kodwa ke, xa usiya evenkileni ehlawula amaphephandaba eBeijing, awufumani manqaku anenkxalabo, kuba amaphephandaba aseTshayina akabonisi ngokuchanileyo iimbono ezahlukahlukeneyo zabantu baseTshayina ngamathuba okukhula koqoqosho lwaseTshayina, kuba amajelo eendaba alawulwa ngamandla yiKomanisi. 
UGqr. Branstad wongezelela esithi elinye lamaphephandaba adumileyo eTshayina alizange livume ukuyikhupha le nqaku kodwa alizange liyichaze igama lalo.
Abahlalutyi bathi iRiphabliki ingade ibenze babe kude nabafazi abavotileyo ngaphambi kokuba kudlule unyulo lwangaphakathi ngenxa yehlazo likaKavanaugh
Abahlalutyi bathi oku kusenokuba sisiphumo sokukhuselwa ngabasemagunyeni abaphezulu kwii-Republican, abaxhasa inkundla yamatyala ka Brett Kavanaugh, okuya kuphumela ekubeni balahlekelwe yinkxaso yabo, ingakumbi phakathi kwabafazi abavota phambi konyulo lonyaka.
Le ngxaki yabangela ukuba abantu abaninzi batsaleleke, ibe uninzi lwabaseRiphablikhi bathi baza kuqhubeka bemphulaphula uKavanaugh.
La mazwi akanakuze aphinde aphinde avuyiswe, utsho uGrant Reeher, isazi ngezentlalo kwezopolitiko kwiSikolo iMaxwell kwiYunivesithi yaseSirakuse, kwiThe Hill.
UReeher wavakalisa amathandabuzo akhe okuba ngaba uphando lwe-FBI olwenziwa ngomzuzu wokugqibela nguSenator waseArizona uJeff Flake, iRiphabhlikhi, luya kukwanela ukuthomalalisa abavoti abacaphukileyo.
