Ngokwengxelo ye-MIC, abanye abaqhankqalazi kwiholo yeSeneti ngoLwesihlanu ekuseni bebetha ingoma ethi, "Iyasondela uNovemba!" ngenxa yokuba iKomiti yezoBulungisa ephantsi kolawulo lwamaRiphabliki igqibe ekubeni ingabuyisi ugqityelo lukaKavanaugh, nangona uDr. Christine Blasey Ford, owayengumgcini-sihlalo weKomiti, wavuma ukuba uyamgqwetha.
"Kuza kubakho ukwanda okuphawulekayo kwintshiseko nentshukumisa yentando yesininzi", utsho njalo uStu Rothenberg, umhlalutyi wezopolitiko ozimeleyo.
Abantu abaninzi bathi wayesele ephezulu kakhulu, ibe kunjalo.
Kodwa kusenokwenzeka ukuba zide nangakumbi, ingakumbi phakathi kwabasetyhini abavota ngaphandle kwamathandabuzo nabaselula (abangama-18-29 ubudala) abahlala ezixekweni, abangenamdla kumongameli kodwa abafane bangavoti.
Ngaphambi kokuba uFord athethe esidlangalaleni, abahlalutyi babesele bexelele abantu ukuba xa eqhubeka nokuxhasa uBrett Kavanaugh njengelungu leNdlu yeNkundla, uya kuphinda abuyele kwiiRiphabliki.
"I-Government is on the wrong side of the Republican Party", utshilo uMichael Steele, owayesakuba ngumphathi weGovernment National Committee, kwi-NBC News ekuqaleni kweveki ephelileyo.
"Oku akujoliswanga nje kuphela kwivoti yeekomiti zeekomiti okanye kuvotelwa kukaKavanaugh, kodwa kwindlela amaRiphabliki awuphethe ngayo lo mba nendlela awaphathana ngayo noFord", utshilo uGuy Cecil, ongumphathi weDemocratic Election Assistance, kwiDemocratic Priorities USA.
Kodwa kubonakala ngathi abantu baseMerika abavumelani ncam ukuba nguFord okanye nguKavanaugh, kuba bona bakholelwa kakhulu kuKavanaugh kunoFord.
Uhlolisiso olutsha olwenziwe ngu-YouGov lubonise ukuba ama-41% abantu abaphendulileyo bathembe ngokupheleleyo okanye kancinane ukuba uFord unobungqina obubambekayo, ngoxa ama-35% abantu abaphendulileyo kuKavanaugh bathi uFord unobungqina obubambekayo.
Ukongezelela, i-38% yabantu abaphendulileyo yathi uKavanaugh usenokuba uyaxoka okanye uyinyani into ayithethileyo, ngoxa i-30% yabantu abaphendulileyo bebesithi yena uFord wayexoka.
Ngenxa yesindululo sikaFlake, i-FBI ngoku iphonononga ubungqina bamabango kaFord, njengoko isenza nomnye umtyholwa kaKavanaugh, uDeborah Ramirez, ngokutsho kweGuardian.
