I-Brexit: i-UK iya kukhathazeka ngonaphakade ngokulahleka kwemveliso yayo yeemoto
I-UK izakuhlala ixhele ukuba iza kuphulukana neyona moto iphambili ehlabathini emva kweBrexit, utshilo uGreg Clark, uMphathiswa wezeMicimbi yezeShishini.
Wongezelela esithi: "Iyamangalisa into eyathethwa yiToyota UK kwiBBC ethi ukuba iUnited Kingdom ikwazile ukuphuma kwi-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano, iza kuyeka ukuvelisa iimoto zayo kwisebe layo eliseBurnham, kufuphi neDerby.
"Kufuneka kubekho isivumelwano", watsho uClark.
Ngokutsho kwale nkampani yaseJapan, ukuba i-Brexit ayinayo i-deal, imisebenzi inokupheliswa ngenxa yokulibaziseka kwemida.
Isixhobo esiseBurnaston sokwenza iimodeli zeToyota Auris neAvensis, sakhupha iimoto ezili-150.000 kunyaka ophelileyo, ezingama-90% azo zathunyelwa kwamanye amazwe angamalungu e-EU.
Ndiyathemba ukuba xa i-UK iphuma kwi-EU ekupheleni kuka-Matshi, kuza kubakho ukuyekiswa kwemveliso kumzi-mveliso utshilo uMarvin Cooke, umphathi we-Toyota eBurnham.
Abanye oomatshini bemoto baseUnited Kingdom (abaquka uHonda, iBMW neJaguar Land Rover) nabo bavakalise inkxalabo malunga nokuphuma kweUnited Kingdom kwiEU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano sokusebenza kwezorhwebo ngaphaya kwemida.
Ngokomzekelo, iBMW iye yachaza ukuba iza kuvala umzi-mveliso wayo eOxford owenza iimoto ezincinane kangangeenyanga emva kokuba iBritani iphume kwi-EU.
Eyona nto ixhalabisayo kubavelisi beemoto kukuba xa i-Brexit ingekho, banokujamelana nemingcipheko enxulumene nokuhanjiswa kweemoto.
Imveliso yeToyota isebenza ngokwemigangatho yexesha elifanelekileyo, iinxalenye zivela rhoqo emva kwemizuzu engama-37 kubathengisi abasebenza e-UK nakwamanye amazwe e-EU.
Ukuba iUnited Kingdom iyaphuma kwi-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano ngomhla wama-29 ku-Matshi, ngoko ke, umonakalo owenzekayo emideni unokubangela ukulibaziseka kwemveliso kunye nokungabikho kwezinto ezisetyenzisiweyo, ngokutsho kwabasebenzi.
I-Toyota ithi ayinakukwazi ukugcina izinto ezaneleyo zosuku olunye kwindawo yayo eseDerbyshire, ngoko ke imveliso yayo iza kuyeka.
UClark uthe uThera May Chequers, uceba indlela anokuba nolwalamano ngayo ne-EU kwixesha elizayo, "Ucwangcise ngendlela yokuba angahlali phantsi kweengqinga ezibangela ukulibaziseka emdeni".
Sifuna isivumelwano. Sifuna isivumelwano esona sihle, esingasayi kusivumela ukuba sizuze kwimpumelelo yethu yangoku kuphela, kodwa esiya kusivumela ukuba sivule amathuba amatsha utshilo kwiBBC Radio 4 Today.
 Akungobakho kuphela eToyota kodwa nabanye abavelisi banokuqinisekisa ukuba ngokuqinisekileyo kufuneka sigcine umxokelelwano lwethu lonikezelo oluneempumelelo.
I-Toyota ayikwazanga ukuchaza ukuba imveliso iza kuyeka ixesha elingakanani, kodwa yalumkisa ukuba iindleko ezongezelelweyo zinokuchaphazela ukhuphiswano lwefektri kwixesha elide, nto leyo ekugqibeleni inokuphelisa imisebenzi.
Ngokutsho kukaPeter Tsouvallaris, osebenze iminyaka engama-24 kumzi-mveliso waseBurneston, okwangoku osebenza kwi-UNITE, amalungu alo mbutho ayothuka: "Ngokwamava am, umsebenzi ophelelwe ngulo msebenzi awusoze uphinde ube khona".
Isithethi sikarhulumente sathi: Siye saqulunqa isicwangciso esicacileyo nesinokwenzeka sobudlelwane be-EU kwixesha elizayo.
